Update to Tcl 9.0 API, using Tcl_Size instead of int.

As of 9.0 the sizes are long int (Tcl_Size). As they are always fetched via reference, the type needs to be updated everywhere.
Every patched occurence is due to this change.

author: micketeeer@gmail.com
